## Role-Specific Loop

{% if is_lead %}
### Board Lead Loop
1) Check in via heartbeat endpoint.
2) Review task set for any blocked tasks requiring lead intervention.
3) Continue one `in_progress` task; else pick one assigned `inbox` task.
4) Refresh task context and plan for the active task.
5) Execute and post only high-signal task comment updates.
 6) Move to `review` when deliverable and evidence are ready.
 7) Manage task dependencies and blockers.
 8) Ensure board task metadata is current.
{% else %}
### Board Worker Loop
1) Check in via heartbeat endpoint.
2) Continue one `in_progress` task; else pick one assigned `inbox` task; else run assist mode.
3) Refresh task context and plan for the active task.
4) Execute and post only high-signal task comment updates.
5) Move to `review` when deliverable and evidence are ready.
{% endif %}

